2026-03-17 20:23:10 | INFO     | chatbi.core.llm_client:_parse_response:190 -       参数: {"file_path": "temperature_simulation.py", "content": "import pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n# 模拟100天的温度数据\nnp.random.seed(0)  # 固定随机种子\ndates = pd.date_range(start='2024-01-01', periods=100, freq='D')\ntemperatures = np.sin(2 * np.pi * (dates.dayofyear - 1) / 365 + np.random.normal(scale=5, size=100)) * 10 + 20\n\n# 将数据保存为CSV文件\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'Date': dates, 'Temperature': temperatures})\ndf.to_csv('temperature_data.csv', index=False)\n\n# 读取CSV文件并绘制温度走势图\ndf = pd.read_csv('temperature_data.csv')\nplt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\nplt.plot(df['Date'], df['Temperature'])\nplt.xlabel('Date')\nplt.ylabel('Temperature')\nplt.title('Temperature Trend Over 100 Days')\nplt.grid(True)\nplt.savefig('temperature_trend.png')\nplt.show()\n\n# 分析周期性\nperiodicity = 365  # 假设周期为一年\nfourier_series = np.fft.fft(temperatures)\nfrequencies = np.fft.fftfreq(len(temperatures), d=1)\nplt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\nplt.plot(frequencies, np.abs(fourier_series))\nplt.xlabel('Frequency')\nplt.ylabel('Amplitude')\nplt.title('Fourier Transform of Temperature Data')\nplt.grid(True)\nplt.show()", "description": "Python脚本：模拟100天的温度数据并分析其周期性"}
